rows.label: qst000511_msg0001
rows.name:
Norman-san, perhaps we
should be going...

rows.label: qst000511_msg0002
rows.name:
You're right... Everyone,
thank you for all your help.

rows.label: qst000511_msg0003
rows.name: But we can't properly thank you here...

rows.label: qst000511_msg0004
rows.name:
If you ever come to Superbia,
please look us up.

rows.label: qst000511_msg0005
rows.name:
Yes, we must show you
our gratitude properly.

rows.label: qst000511_msg0006
rows.name:
We will never forget this
kindness. I promise.

rows.label: qst000511_msg0007
rows.name: Thank you again. You saved us.
